##build the image
docker build -t psrtiming:base .

##build the container
docker run -d -p 222:22 -v ~/Desktop/:/home/psr/work --name tempo2-mcc psrtiming:base

##connect the container 
ssh -X -p 222 psr@localhost

passwd: psr

######
There will some errors when login in
1. X11 forwarding request failed on channel 0

    https://www.cyberciti.biz/faq/how-to-fix-x11-forwarding-request-failed-on-channel-0/
    
    In Ubuntu is not 'sshd' but 'ssh'
    So please run
    /etc/init.d/ssh reload

2. "X11 proxy: wrong authorisation protocol attempted"
    cp /home/psr/.Xauthority /root/

3. if you want to run with tempo2, there will be some errors will no pgplot
server.
So you need to run this before you run tempo2:
    /usr/bin/./pgxwin_server &
Or you can add this to the ~/.bashrc file then pgxserver will auto run when
you login in.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
All this will need root
So login root by
    docker exec -it container-name /bin/bash
Like:
    docker exec -it tempo2-mcc /bin/bash
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
